  PreLevelDialogue:
  - How would you define modern art?
  - "No I don\u2019t think bland is the right word, I would say\u2026 Inspired."
  - Yeah, inspired!
  - "Well we\u2019ve got a very inspired family who want some. You think you can
    manage that?"
  - "Hey I mean it might be a nice change of pace! I\u2019m not hiding anything\u2026"
  - "Okay look, the last sculpture in the order might be a little more challenging,
    but you\u2019ll survive."
  - "Hey! Don\u2019t disrespect the buy 2 get 1 free business model! It\u2019s served
    us well so far hasn\u2019t it?"
  - Just go make Bill proud already!
